Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Halifax, December 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,1917. The harbor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A munitionship drifts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the pier
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,burning. Thousands of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,people stop to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,watch. They press
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,their faces to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,windows. They walk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,waterfront. They have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,no idea what's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on board. A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,telegraph operator named
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vince Coleman knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A sailor has
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just told him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he's already running
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for safety alongside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,his coworker, then
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,stops. He turns
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,around. There's a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,passenger train coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,300 people who
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,don't know what's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,alone. He sends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,one last message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,train. Ammunitionship a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,fire in harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this will
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,be my last
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,message. Goodbye, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,20 seconds later,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,2 ,000 tons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of TNT detonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The largest man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,made explosion in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,history until Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma. A wave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of glass crosses
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the city. Every
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,window facing the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,harbor. 249 people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,lose an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that morning. 16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,lose both. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the water comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A wall of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,harbor, 18 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,high. It crosses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Dartmouth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shore and erases
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the MIG -Maw
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,village at Tufts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cove, a community
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that had lived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,1800 die, 300
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,live. He never
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,knows.
